{"tid":251652,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[女子組格鬥]海之戀美女代理又打架　互飛腳扯頭髮","createTime":"2017-05-21T06:28:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-21T12:51:47.000Z","uid":54373,"like":25,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"09b8e70d80cabfd0bf40cf8fcae0ace3523a59b4","tid":251652,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T06:28:13.000Z","msg":"消息指，這單打鬥是在今日中午左右發生，地點是廣東道龍堡酒店門口。片段所見，有四名女子互相打鬥，其中三名女子應是同一組人，向一名灰衫女人拳打腳踢，該女人被踢中最少四腳，即使作出還擊，仍難以一敵三，被三女打到推埋牆差點跌落地，有人打到連樓盤宣傳單張及卡片都跌落地。<br />\n<br />\n打鬥期間，粗口橫飛。灰衫女爆粗指，「你咪X走呀肥婆」，黑衫女則怒罵，「關你X事咩」，灰衫女接住鬧，「你肥唔係關我X事，但係你整我就關我X事」，又指罵對方三個蝦一個。灰衫女隨即報警，警方事後到場調查。<br />\n<br />\n有前綫經理直言，生活逼人，「呢個盤周圍打架呀」，<span style=\"color: red;\">海之戀已淪為地產經紀爭生意格鬥場。</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/21/142804_7ad69e3f5329e9f38e023c8db91b40b3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F21%2F142804_7ad69e3f5329e9f38e023c8db91b40b3.jpg&h=e4d2c9f0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/21/142805_1b7f3a1cf0f150b7c7661d2155d97d32.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F21%2F142805_1b7f3a1cf0f150b7c7661d2155d97d32.jpg&h=c17ed30d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/21/142806_f6118a610b8ff3673410235f02bd75a3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F21%2F142806_f6118a610b8ff3673410235f02bd75a3.jpg&h=5dce6a54&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a4370592a02b32c0b310d11f691f1f4bf1c0fa4f","tid":251652,"uid":37528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T06:31:03.000Z","msg":"超重量級<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58cea06a07fad9dcf5386b058c5c3e021bd419f2","tid":251652,"uid":70439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T06:31:24.000Z","msg":"美極<img src=\"/assets/f